      "text_excerpt": "High-resolution professional VR headsets | Vrgineers.com\nNext-Generation Pilot Training\nWe deliver next-generation virtual and mixed reality training systems for professional and military clients.\nXTAL\nThe XTAL MR/VR headsets have been developed and designed for pilot training.\nmore\nSomnium\nSomnium VR/MR headsets deliver premium quality for immersive, extended training sessions.\nmore\nPilot Trainers\nOur Trainers offer unlimited training with unlimited aircraft types and scenarios.\nmore\nTraining Facilities\nOur cutting-edge training facilities are tailored to meet a diverse range of needs and preferences.\nmore\nOur Clients\nNews\nIntroducing a new NVG-inspired Visual Layer in th...\nNight operations demand precision, adaptability, and consistent training conditions. To support this, we have introduced a new NVG-inspired visual layer in our VRG Tool, designe...\nmore\nApril 22, 2026\nNew VRG Tool\nAfter intensive development, we are proud to present the latest VRG Tool 4.0.0, which brings significant improvements to the way you work with your headsets, making setup and co...\nmore\nApril 8, 2025\nPrime Minister Fiala at Vrgineers: Czech technolo...\nVrgineers had the honour to present its technologies to the Prime Minister of the Czech Republic. Prime Minister Petr Fiala met with the company's management and also tried out ...\nmore\nMarch 4, 2025"
    },
    "about": {
      "url": "https://www.vrgineers.com/about",
      "text": "About Us | Vrgineers.com\nAbout Us\nVrgineers, founded in 2017 by Marek Polcak and Etnetera Group, represented by Martin Holecko a Vaclav Bittner, is a leader in developing immersive technologies.\nUnder the leadership of Marek Polcak as the CEO, the company offers high-quality and effective military pilot training using advanced XTAL Virtual and Mixed Reality headsets and aviation simulators.\nVrgineers is at the forefront of cutting-edge simulation technologies, with a team of experts in virtual and mixed reality dedicated to creating immersive tools for professionals and military clients.\nThe company is involved in extensive research, development, manufacturing, and integration of advanced virtual and mixed simulators.\nOur ultimate goal is to bridge the gap between simulation and reality, ensuring the safety of professionals in their real-life endeavors.\nMarek Polcak\nChief Executive Officer\nJiri Zvachta\nChief Financial Officer\nMartin Chloupek\nChief Technology Officer\nAntonin Posusta\nHead of Software Development\nJan Mravinac\nHead of Manufacturing\nRoman Balaz\nVice President\nKrystof Slavik\nHead of Firmware Development\nJakub Rubas\nHead of Technical Support\nJakub Frolec\nHead of Electronical Engineering\nJan Machac\nDelivery Manager\nMarek Boskovic\nHead of Mechanical Engineering\nLegal Counsel\nDavid Strapac\nLegal & Operations Manager\nBrian Gottesman\nGabell Beaver\nExternal Legal Counsel"
